<p>Please let me know if I can help in any other way!</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1265740" data-commentid="1265740" data-postid="194666" data-belowelement="div-comment-1265740" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Tieghan" aria-label="Reply to Tieghan">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
