				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<b class="fn">Hana</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/freezer-breakfast-sandwiches/#comment-1265964"><time datetime="2026-04-17T06:33:02-06:00">April 17, 2026 at 6:33 AM</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I think the comment about missing steps is because they are listed 1, 2, 4 in the recipe.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1265964" data-commentid="1265964" data-postid="194666" data-belowelement="div-comment-1265964" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Hana" aria-label="Reply to Hana">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
