		<li id="comment-1265582" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1 parent">
			<article id="div-comment-1265582" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<b class="fn">Lane</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/freezer-breakfast-sandwiches/#comment-1265582"><time datetime="2026-04-14T10:50:53-06:00">April 14, 2026 at 10:50 AM</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating perfmatters-lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;80&#039;%20height=&#039;16&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%2080%2016&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="2 stars" width="80" height="16" data-src="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-2.svg" /><br />
The chicken patties were really dry and did not stick together well. I would probably add a little bit of fat like oil and a binder like egg to them since chicken has very little fat. I also thought the eggs were dry, I would probably add more milk. We ate these right away, I feel like freezing and reheating will dry them out even more.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1265582" data-commentid="1265582" data-postid="194666" data-belowelement="div-comment-1265582" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Lane" aria-label="Reply to Lane">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		<ol class="children">
		<li id="comment-1265600" class="comment byuser comment-author-halfbakedharvest bypostauthor even depth-2 staff">
			<article id="div-comment-1265600" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<b class="fn">Tieghan</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/freezer-breakfast-sandwiches/#comment-1265600"><time datetime="2026-04-14T13:18:14-06:00">April 14, 2026 at 1:18 PM</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks for sharing your feedback, Lane. Sorry to hear these were not a favorite! Have a great day!</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1265600" data-commentid="1265600" data-postid="194666" data-belowelement="div-comment-1265600" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Tieghan" aria-label="Reply to Tieghan">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
