						<a href="https://www.halfbakedharvest.com/freezer-breakfast-sandwiches/#comment-1265597"><time datetime="2026-04-14T13:15:54-06:00">April 14, 2026 at 1:15 PM</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Hey Allison,<br />
Thanks for asking! So sorry, the steps are just mis-numbered, step 3 is not missing:) I like to use the Smeg if I toast my English muffins first, but it&#8217;s not necessary if you don&#8217;t want to do that.</p>
<p>I hope you love these sandwiches!</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1265597" data-commentid="1265597" data-postid="194666" data-belowelement="div-comment-1265597" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Tieghan" aria-label="Reply to Tieghan">Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
